snippet.title: Hattke
snippet.description:
Hattke is the entertainment channel owned by Rusk Media Pvt Limited that you should look for. Hattke is the way we think. It is the way we see things. Hattke is the way we create and consume entertainment. Hattke is the entertainment channel that you should be looking out for!
 
From tantalising Bollywood choreographies that make you thumak to hit Hindi songs to stepping up your dance game at all those sangeets you have to attend, this channel is your one-stop solution to every dance, music and entertainment. From live dance performances to music fests, this channel is your one stop-solution for all things entertainment.
 
Our aim is to build a community of creators who steadily build a strong audience with their talent, collaborate with them and encourage them to showcase anything that makes them Hattke from others!
